Package civitas.celestis.util.group

Class Pair<T>

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.util.group.Pair<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of objects held by the pair.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Group<T>, Iterable<T>
public class Pair<T> extends Object implements Group<T>

Pair

The Pair class represents a simple group of two objects. It implements the Group interface, providing methods to work with a pair of objects as a unit. This class is a basic building block for organizing and manipulating two related objects together.
